  "text": "The demonstration of a highly ordered and conserved microbiome is relevant to many lung disorders [CITATION_1] , particularly the respiratory infections that take 4 million lives annually [CITATION_2] ). There is a marked change of structure with fragmentation of major networks in the smokers, but high conservation of network membership between asthmatics and the whole cohort.",
